             was indicted for <rs id="t18000528-87-off501" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000528-87-off501" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000528-87-off501" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000528-87-cd502" type="crimeDate">3d of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-87-off501 t18000528-87-cd502"></join>, a bed-tick, value 12s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000528-87-victim909" type="victimName">
                     George 
